  <section class="intro">
    <h1>We make thoughtful digital products.</h1>
    <p class="subheader">As designers, we're responsible for what we bring into the world. Those things should be thoughtful.</p>
    <p>We're hired to think through problems. We ask why. We iteratively discover the product. We talk to users. Strategy matters to us. Oh, and the beautiful interfaces? They’re by-products of doing good work.</p>
    <p>When we’re not building products, we’re teaching others to do the same, by <a href="http://designpaloalto.com">hosting community events</a> to inspire others, or mentoring the next generation of designers.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="team" name="about" id="about">
