        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-profile paul">
        <div class="profile-photo"></div>
        <div class="profile-overview">
          <a class="button button-material button-action button-twitter" href="http://twitter.com/brim" target="_blank"></a>
          <h3>Paul Mederos</h3>
          <p>Paul leads product design at <a href="http://mypowersupply.com" target="_blank">Power Supply</a>. He specializes in behavior design (making and breaking habits), product management, interface design, &amp; prototyping.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

